  There's nothing like a bad haircut to really put a damper on your confidence. (Not even celebrities are immune to them.) A bad haircut can mean wearing a hat for a few weeks while your strands grow out. Or it can mean crying in the shower while running your hands through your newly cut locks. Either way, it can make you want to crawl into a hole until you regrow those lost centimetres. Now, we're fully aware of the fact that bad haircuts aren't the end of the world ― there are far worse things to worry about ― but no matter how you slice snip it, they really do suck. These folks on Twitter would most definitely agree: Share this slide: